  "detailed_description": "<h1>Try the DOG version!</h1><p></p><br><h1>A New Unique Shy Cats is Coming!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>The Hidden Orchestra is on tour!  <br>They're <strong>cute</strong>. They're <strong>chibi</strong>. They're talented. But, they're <strong>shy</strong>!<br><br>They are trapped in ice! in sand! Even in other planets!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295570/extras/408c3889d6250d0b0b3d4c671550ef92.poster.avif?t=1710789532\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295570/extras/408c3889d6250d0b0b3d4c671550ef92.webm?t=1710789532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295570/extras/408c3889d6250d0b0b3d4c671550ef92.mp4?t=1710789532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>In this hidden object game you will need to find hidden musician cats that are embarassed to play their music. <br><br>For every cat you find, you will hear a different musical instrument sound. <br><br><strong>Make your own music!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295570/extras/0203d6f9952ce2b420854f5a98e2324f.poster.avif?t=1710789532\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295570/extras/0203d6f9952ce2b420854f5a98e2324f.webm?t=1710789532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2295570/extras/0203d6f9952ce2b420854f5a98e2324f.mp4?t=1710789532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.",
